snippet.title: PlayStation - Mystic Mind - Yureru Omoi (1998) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Mystic Mind: Yureru Omoi is an Adventure game, developed by Family Soft and published by Mycom, which was released in Japan in 1998.
